<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demande de participation - ${nomEvenement}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .logo-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .event-title {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .request-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .motivation-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        .personal-info {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .reminder-message {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .contact-info {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="logo-section">
        <img src="https://veevent.vercel.app/veevent.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="event-title">Demande de participation</h1>
        <h2 style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; margin: 0;">${nomEvenement}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="request-text">
        <p>Bonjour,</p>

        <p>Une nouvelle personne souhaite rejoindre l'évènement : <strong>${nomEvenement}</strong>.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="personal-info">
        <h3 style="color: #3498db; margin-top: 0;">Info du participant :</h3>
        <p><strong>&#x1F464; Nom :</strong> ${nom}</p>
        <p><strong>&#x1F464; Prénom :</strong> ${prenom}</p>
        <p><strong>&#x1F4E7; Email :</strong> ${emailExpediteur}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reminder-message">
        &#x26A0;&#xFE0F; Pensez à accepter ou rejeter la demande.
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info">
        &#x1F4C5; Candidature envoyée le ${dateEnvoi}
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
